       END-TASK.
      *    add exit specific code
      *
       SYNCPOINT.
      *    add exit specific code
      *
       SYNCPOINT-ROLLBACK.
      *    add exit specific code
      *
       AT-ERROR.
      *    add exit specific code
      *
       SHUTDOWN.
      *    add exit specific code
      *    Perform all shut routines
      *    Ensure that all files are closed
      *    Ensure that all dynamic memory is freed
      *
       SET-ADDRESS.
	   IF EXIT-IN-TASK
	       SET ADDRESS OF CICSICB TO EXIT-ICB
	       SET ADDRESS OF EIBLK TO EXIT-EIBLK
	   END-IF
